data.description: Welcome to your new home in Mayfair.! This home has a foyer entrance with a spacious living room/ dining room and kitchen. Hardwood floors are featured in the living room and dining room areas. There is a large deck for those outside bbq's. There are 3 nice-sized bedrooms with ample storage and closet space. Finished basement with a full bath , separate laundry and work bench area. Street parking or rear parking.
